# RAG physical tuning (greenfield)

## Quick start

```bash
docker compose up -d postgres
export DATABASE_URL=postgresql://rag:rag@localhost:5433/rag
uv sync
uv run python scripts/migrate.py
uv run uvicorn rag.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 --app-dir src
```

`POST /chunks` ingests with a random unit vector of dimension 768 (demo). `POST /retrieve` runs vector search with tunable `ef_search` / `ivfflat.probes` from active profile.

See `config/profiles.yaml` and `config/tuner_guardrails.yaml`.
